metadata.name: Entrañas
metadata.description:
A genesis piece created for my first collection on foundation, titled "entrañas". Through my eyes, I see "through" you... inside and out. You show people your true color, and this is how I see them.

The owner of this piece will also be entitled 2 whitelist spots from [Ugly People](https://twitter.com/UglyPeopleNFT) collection and an OG role in our private discord community.
